<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-93-0424 </DOCNO><TEXT>The development of the Gullfaks field includes three giant gravity basedplatforms and subsea wells. This paper describes the field, the drillingprogram and the drilling equipment installed on the platforms. Shallowgas and abnormal pore pressure are among the challenges the operatorfaces. The block was awarded to a group comprising Statoil, the operator(85%), Norsk Hydro (9%) and Saga Petroleum (6%) in 1978. Explorationdrilling commenced the same year.</TEXT></DOC>